Package com.sysag_cds.world

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Building
    A Building in a Location
    BuildingFactory
    Factory Class which returns Building instances.It keeps a list of generated instances
    Business
    Business Agent to whom other Person agents go for different reasons.
    BusinessFactory
    Factory Class that creates Business Agents in the current container in different buildings.
    Location
    A place in the map
    RandomBuilding
    Returns a random Building from the World Singleton or from a Building List with or without removing it
    RandomBusiness
    Returns a random Business category given the specified probability distribution.
    Road
    A Road in a Location
    RoadFactory
    Factory Class that generates Road instances
    World
    A Class with a single instance (singleton) that represents a map in which the simulation takes place.
